{"tid":502560,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"報Vacation Scheme報到好苦惱","createTime":"2017-12-18T04:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T05:08:32.000Z","uid":120774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0aa5a088a2e497f3166e0843334fafb2f9250f","tid":502560,"uid":120774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"讀緊LLB, penultimate year, 依家去緊一年英國exchange<br />\n去到12月中，終於醒覺要搵工<br />\n雖然以依家GPA黎睇都穩陣有FT PCLL Offer, 但係對未來真係完全睇唔透<br />\n其實我真係唔係咁想做Solicitor，但奈何屋企環境唔算好，如果要做Counsel的話頭半年會完全冇收入，之後仲要負擔埋辦事處租金，真係唔忍心攞屋企既經濟狀況教飛。<br />\n咁冇辦法啦，惟有Vacation Scheme同Mini-pupillage都報下，睇下有咩出路。但係愈報就愈灰，發覺自己一直以來浪費左好多時間，冇真係好好讀書，依家連要填一個Academic Referee都諗唔到有一個熟既tutor可以幫手。<br />\n我真係好迷惘，究竟我可以點做？我應該揀solicitor定barrister好？"},{"pid":"df443f907f85a637e366145bc1332cd09521b321","tid":502560,"uid":120774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"law firm 會唔會因為我唔係香港而in都唔in我㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82057810adf36f8d0208dec822609a2e7bbff1cf","tid":502560,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"如果有能力入到temple/dvc咪去做counsel<br />\n唔係既頭一年真係挨得幾辛苦，聽過有人無錢交租要問屋企人借錢"},{"pid":"a9ada62ffc914bd3f72c5e73a3a8b4ea1c22d683","tid":502560,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"btw你話屋企環境唔算好<br />\n但係阿媽有HSBC Premier<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45920f91de0ea73e941f5997f6ba62162747b2f7","tid":502560,"uid":120774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw你話屋企環境唔算好<br />\n但係阿媽有HSBC Premier<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上做按揭就夠開premier，姐係仲差銀行錢"},{"pid":"d708384f3cca86334e910708d3079e07abeba788","tid":502560,"uid":120774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:08:32.000Z